		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The "FFE" aka Super Magic Card doesn't simulate other mappers at all, you must port all games to it's mapper. See this recent topic: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://nesdev.com/bbs/viewtopic.php?p=15072">http://nesdev.com/bbs/viewtopic.php?p=15072</a><!-- m -->

		

